  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DungeonGOGO</strong> is a challenging precision platformer where you escape from the Light Prison and rescue your friends from hidden chambers.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and uncover all the secret rooms to set your friends free.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalistic graphics</strong> for a clean and focused experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly challenging gameplay</strong> that will test your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40 levels</strong> and <strong>20 secrets</strong> to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full <strong>controller support</strong> for an immersive playstyle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is hardcore—try not to break your controller! 🙂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you see this symbol:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700610/extras/5ae44ad8a666da6a9475c9404c89fce2.avif?t=1735487726\" width=332 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a closer look—there’s a secret nearby...</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DungeonGOGO</strong> is a challenging precision platformer where you escape from the Light Prison and rescue your friends from hidden chambers.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and uncover all the secret rooms to set your friends free.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalistic graphics</strong> for a clean and focused experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly challenging gameplay</strong> that will test your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40 levels</strong> and <strong>20 secrets</strong> to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full <strong>controller support</strong> for an immersive playstyle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is hardcore—try not to break your controller! 🙂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you see this symbol:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700610/extras/5ae44ad8a666da6a9475c9404c89fce2.avif?t=1735487726\" width=332 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a closer look—there’s a secret nearby...</p>",
